  "detailed_description": "This game is a challenging physics-based 2D-platformer about climbing a mountain using only a barrel, a double-barrel and lots of ammo.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy controls</h2>Only the mouse is used for control:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Move the mouse to aim the double-barrel.<br></li><li>Press the mouse keys to shoot and fly away from the recoil.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/73cb4ecba10b48a9144e20173df2897e.poster.avif?t=1715191249\" width=614 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/73cb4ecba10b48a9144e20173df2897e.webm?t=1715191249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/73cb4ecba10b48a9144e20173df2897e.mp4?t=1715191249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exciting challenge</h2>Almost any mistake can cost you a huge part of progress. Practice, make mistakes and eventually you will be able to overcome all the obstacles.<br><br>On average, it takes 2-3 hours to get through the game, but if you practice enough, you can complete it in just 5-10 minutes.<br><br>Test your skills, reaction speed and patience in this frustrating game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/61f11ecb8d8467e685a37099e780a84b.poster.avif?t=1715191249\" width=614 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/61f11ecb8d8467e685a37099e780a84b.webm?t=1715191249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/61f11ecb8d8467e685a37099e780a84b.mp4?t=1715191249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "This game is a challenging physics-based 2D-platformer about climbing a mountain using only a barrel, a double-barrel and lots of ammo.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy controls</h2>Only the mouse is used for control:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Move the mouse to aim the double-barrel.<br></li><li>Press the mouse keys to shoot and fly away from the recoil.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/73cb4ecba10b48a9144e20173df2897e.poster.avif?t=1715191249\" width=614 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/73cb4ecba10b48a9144e20173df2897e.webm?t=1715191249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/73cb4ecba10b48a9144e20173df2897e.mp4?t=1715191249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exciting challenge</h2>Almost any mistake can cost you a huge part of progress. Practice, make mistakes and eventually you will be able to overcome all the obstacles.<br><br>On average, it takes 2-3 hours to get through the game, but if you practice enough, you can complete it in just 5-10 minutes.<br><br>Test your skills, reaction speed and patience in this frustrating game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/61f11ecb8d8467e685a37099e780a84b.poster.avif?t=1715191249\" width=614 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/61f11ecb8d8467e685a37099e780a84b.webm?t=1715191249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908140/extras/61f11ecb8d8467e685a37099e780a84b.mp4?t=1715191249\"